review.reviewBody: Tried their honey garlic parmesan Wings, and Mozzarella Sticks for first time  and they were phenomenal! Never had such good wings before. The mozzarella sticks were a fantastic appetizer, with a golden, crunchy exterior and gooey, melty cheese inside. Both dishes were superbly executed and absolutely delicious!
Honey Garlic Parmesan is chefs kiss. Usually prefer boneless chicken but the bone-in option here is better

Fantastic Food ...so many flavour options all for a reasonable price and top it off with incredible ownership who always go above and beyond. This is our go-to for take-out especially when friends come into town that don't have this luxury - many of them order to take home with them...DELICIOUS!!
So amazing!! Went above and beyond with their service!! Taste was so good will 100% reorder
Amazing service and the best pizza, wings and fries in town! Owner is a gem!
